{"data":{"type":"discussions","id":"2125","attributes":{"title":"Can an owner of a Discord server ban/demote a staff JUST for doing their job?","slug":"2125-can-an-owner-of-a-discord-server-bandemote-a-staff-just-for-doing-their-job","commentCount":10,"participantCount":7,"createdAt":"2023-02-28T19:39:48+00:00","lastPostedAt":"2023-05-01T14:35:05+00:00","lastPostNumber":10,"canReply":true,"canRename":false,"canDelete":false,"canHide":false,"isApproved":true,"isSticky":false,"canSticky":false,"isLocked":false,"canLock":false,"canTag":false,"canSeeReactions":true,"canMerge":false},"relationships":{"posts":{"data":[{"type":"posts","id":"50064"},{"type":"posts","id":"50065"},{"type":"posts","id":"50066"},{"type":"posts","id":"50067"},{"type":"posts","id":"50068"},{"type":"posts","id":"50069"},{"type":"posts","id":"50070"},{"type":"posts","id":"50071"},{"type":"posts","id":"50078"},{"type":"posts","id":"50381"}]},"tags":{"data":[{"type":"tags","id":"4"}]},"poll":{"data":{"type":"polls","id":"157"}}}},"included":[{"type":"posts","id":"50064","attributes":{"number":1,"createdAt":"2023-02-28T19:39:48+00:00","contentType":"comment","contentHtml":"<p>One question: Can an owner of a Discord server ban/demote a staff JUST for doing their job?</p>\n\n<blockquote class=\"uncited\"><div><p><em>NOTE: I AM JUST ASKING BECAUSE IT SEEMS WEIRD TO ME. I DON'T WANT THE DELAYED TURN TO COME NOW TO INSULT OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT. I'M JUST ASKING BECAUSE IT DOESN'T SQUARE ME. SO ANSWER ME IN A GOOD WAY</em></p></div></blockquote>\n\n<p>I am a staff of a Discord server. And they gave me a warn for doing my job. Look at these.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://drama.gg/assets/files/2023-02-28/1677612260-75905-image.png\" title=\"\"><br>\nRules for staffs:<br>\nDO NOT CREATE CHANNELS WITHOUT PERMISSION<br>\nThis seems logical to me, because the server has a structure and if channels started to be created it would be chaos.</p>\n\n<p>DO NOT CREATE THREADS. ADD REACTIONS, OR SEND MESSAGES IN #WELCOME</p>\n\n<p>I can understand this about the messages, but the threads or reactions do NOT make sense.</p>\n\n<p>DO NOT WRITE TO (x channels)<br>\nUNLESS THE FOUNDER GIVES YOU PERMISSION</p>\n\n<p>Same as before, I get it.</p>\n\n<p>DO NOT ADD ROLES.</p>\n\n<p>This is indeed incredible. I mean, you can't create roles, when your role system is a dogshit?</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Well, each owner decides the rules, but I see that server with a lot of potential, but the lack of competition from the owner is ruining it.</p>\n\n<p>Well, read this for yourselves.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://drama.gg/assets/files/2023-02-28/1677612982-204562-image.png\" title=\"\"></p>\n\n<p>how old are you have<br>\nyou have*<br>\n12 years old<br>\ndamn, what a fucking kid</p>\n\n\n\n<p>I'm not saying anything else, he's a 12 yo bullshit kid trying to make a server, but if he doesn't let the staff do their job, I don't think he's going to do well.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>ùñåùñÜùñôùñîùñïùñäùñòùñÜùñîùñî</p>","editedAt":"2023-02-28T19:43:23+00:00","canEdit":false,"canDelete":false,"canHide":false,"canLike":true,"canFlag":true,"isApproved":true,"canApprove":false,"canReact":true},"relationships":{"discussion":{"data":{"type":"discussions","id":"2125"}},"user":{"data":{"type":"users","id":"7110"}},"editedUser":{"data":{"type":"users","id":"7110"}},"likes":{"data":[]},"mentionedBy":{"data":[{"type":"posts","id":"50068"},{"type":"posts","id":"50070"}]},"reactions":{"data":[]}}},{"type":"posts","id":"50068","attributes":{"number":5,"createdAt":"2023-02-28T23:42:07+00:00","contentType":"comment","contentHtml":"<blockquote class=\"uncited\"><div><p><a href=\"https://drama.gg/d/2125/1\" class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"50064\">donttellmeanything</a> One question: Can an owner of a Discord server ban/demote a staff JUST for doing their job?</p></div></blockquote>\n\n<p>yes, yes they can. it's not a real job and you have no rights on discord, its simply a role the owner removed from you, its absolutely worthless</p>","canEdit":false,"canDelete":false,"canHide":false,"canLike":true,"canFlag":true,"isApproved":true,"canApprove":false,"canReact":true},"relationships":{"user":{"data":{"type":"users","id":"3132"}},"discussion":{"data":{"type":"discussions","id":"2125"}},"likes":{"data":[]},"mentionedBy":{"data":[]},"reactions":{"data":[]}}},{"type":"posts","id":"50070","attributes":{"number":7,"createdAt":"2023-03-01T22:38:07+00:00","contentType":"comment","contentHtml":"<p><a href=\"https://drama.gg/d/2125/1\" class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"50064\">donttellmeanything</a> <br>\nAt the end of the day, the owner (or the larping title of \"CEO\" on discord) decides everything.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://drama.gg/assets/files/2023-03-01/1677710190-815668-image.png\" title=\"\"></p>\n\n","canEdit":false,"canDelete":false,"canHide":false,"canLike":true,"canFlag":true,"isApproved":true,"canApprove":false,"canReact":true},"relationships":{"user":{"data":{"type":"users","id":"7004"}},"discussion":{"data":{"type":"discussions","id":"2125"}},"likes":{"data":[]},"mentionedBy":{"data":[]},"reactions":{"data":[]}}},{"type":"posts","id":"50065","attributes":{"number":2,"createdAt":"2023-02-28T19:42:39+00:00","contentType":"comment","contentHtml":"<p>I forgot, by the way.<br>\n(I know there are HUNDREDS of servers that do this, but it gives admin LITERALLY TO WHOEVER ASKS IT)</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://drama.gg/assets/files/2023-02-28/1677613305-123034-image.png\" title=\"\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://drama.gg/assets/files/2023-02-28/1677613327-460448-image.png\" title=\"\"></p>\n\n\n\n<p>something that I wanted to add as data</p>","canEdit":false,"canDelete":false,"canHide":false,"canLike":true,"canFlag":true,"isApproved":true,"canApprove":false,"canReact":true},"relationships":{"discussion":{"data":{"type":"discussions","id":"2125"}},"user":{"data":{"type":"users","id":"7110"}},"likes":{"data":[]},"mentionedBy":{"data":[]},"reactions":{"data":[]}}},{"type":"posts","id":"50066","attribute